<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #EF4444; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
        .button { background: #EF4444; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .error { background: #FEE2E2; border-left: 4px solid #EF4444; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
            <div class="error">
                <strong>We were unable to process your payment.</strong>
            </div>
            <p>Unfortunately, your recent payment failed. This could be due to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Insufficient funds</li>
                <li>Expired card</li>
                <li>Bank decline</li>
                <li>Incorrect billing information</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Please update your payment method to continue using Flowvera without interruption.</p>
            <a href="{{billingUrl}}" class="button">Update Payment Method</a>
            <p>If you need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
            <p><strong>The Flowvera Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Flowvera. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
